description: Prosecutors say there is no evidence the adult male was held against his will, as the woman is freed.
title: Stockholm mother no longer suspected of imprisoning son
title_page: Stockholm mother no longer suspected of imprisoning son - BBC News
maintext: Opening the unlocked door, she said she found the flat in darkness and reeking of urine, decay, dirt and dust. There was no answer when she shouted "hello" so she went in, picking her way through mounds of clutter.
